==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chevy
<hw>Chev"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>chivy</asp>, and <asp>chivvy</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[Prob. fr. the
ballad of <ets>Chevy Chase</ets>; cf. Prov. E. <ets>chevychase</ets> a
noise, confusion, pursuit.]</ety> <mark>[Eng.]</mark> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
cry used in hunting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A hunt; chase; pursuit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The game of prisoners' base. See <er>Base</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, 24.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chevvy</ent>⟦br⟧
